{"tid":2011740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯23項人大政協建議及提案 包括倡珠海建香港城","createTime":"2020-05-11T08:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T09:15:29.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3e236eb0c0dd74e0608ac6a9c0a1718202f963","tid":2011740,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"民建聯23項人大政協建議及提案 包括倡珠海建香港城<br />\n2020-05-11 HKT 15:50<br />\n<br />\n全國兩會將於本月下旬召開，民建聯的全國人大代表及政協委員將提出23項建議及提案。<br />\n<br />\n在公共衛生方面，民建聯建議提高應對突發重大公共衞生能力，包括檢討疫情通報交流機制、提升防疫裝備及物資的製造能力，鼓勵研製可重用口罩等。此外，亦建議成立專責機構推廣中國文化，加強對香港青少年、大專及中小學老師認識中國歷史及國情。<br />\n<br />\n其他建議及提案包括，在珠海市桂山島及港珠澳大橋珠海段南側指定水域建香港城，以提供大量住屋單位；此外研究立法全面禁止食用貓狗，訂立阻嚇性處則。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525480-20200511.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525480-20200511.htm&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=76ebb835\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525480-20200511.htm&h=10420ba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525480-20200511.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d6224f55c7e9bb03222ad1249a86309d6e9cecaa","tid":2011740,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推廣完仲反得勁"},{"pid":"cc3f98f7bf9231b3bf52fd1526c537392dde0872","tid":2011740,"uid":39200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"其實講到支那咁好, 做咩成日幻想整幾個香港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccd9fd6f3999b0ecb5a5885127135021a5a73ff","tid":2011740,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲禁食貓狗架咩？"},{"pid":"2daf7b2059d9dcca94f22ea7d5765a32e4358d44","tid":2011740,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite